3. Strong Copyleft Obligations
The NFLv1.1 is a reciprocal license. To ensure the software remains free and open:

3.1 License Consistency: Any Derivative Work that you distribute or provide via SaaS must be licensed under this same License (NFLv1.1) or any later version of the NextFerret License.

3.2 Source Code Availability: If you distribute the Work, you must make the complete, machine-readable source code available to recipients.

3.3 Network Use (SaaS): Providing access via a network is considered Distribution. You must make the source code available to all users interacting with it.

