6. Usage Restrictions (The "No-Gatekeep" Clause)
6.1 Prohibited Jurisdictions: This License automatically terminates and prohibits the use, distribution, or installation of the Work within any jurisdiction that requires, by law, age verification or government-id-linked identity checks to access or run an Operating System.
6.2 Intent: This software is intended to be a free and open platform. Any state-mandated barrier to entry at the OS level is considered a breach of the fundamental freedom of this software.

